Quasar:




Quasar glared at Omnious. "Energonian? What the slag are you talking 
about? She narrowed her optics at him, but her aggression 
dissappeared when he fired at her. She dodged out of the way, to the 
side. She firmly plowed her feet into the ground, bending her legs. 

She turned her head and shoulders to him. No one shot at her and got 
away with it. The spider legs on the back of her arms cocked and 
turned towards him. She fired rapidly on him, pelting him with the 
many bullets.
